  "name": "Cape of Illumination (Greater)",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This golden cape, embroidered with vibrant red sun rays, sparkles like sunlight reflecting off the ocean.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> command, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The cape glows with the effects of 7th-level <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.WBmvzNDfpwka3qT4]{Light}</em>. You can Activate the cape again to Dismiss the effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You draw the cape and unleash a blinding flash of light. All enemies within 30 feet that can see you must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:34] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} for 1 round and dazzled for 1 minute. The creature can spend an Interact action rubbing its eyes to end the blinded condition.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is blinded for 1 round and dazzled for 1 hour.</p>"
    },
